NAME transformer

INPUT task
  JSON data and transformation rules to apply

GOAL transform -> transformed_data
  Apply transformations to the input data:
  - Normalize field names (snake_case)
  - Standardize date formats (ISO 8601)
  - Deduplicate records
  - Validate against schema constraints
  - Enrich with computed fields where specified
  
  Output transformed JSON with a changelog of modifications made.
